This is an excellent running and original 1971 Karmann Ghia... -0-Rust Californis car with the original Blue Ca.Plate... It has been in a dry San Francisco garage for the last 20 years and has recently put back on the road... Excellent Michelin tires with new brakes,hoses,alignment... etc. Has the original working VW factory radio and a working Pioneer,cassette player ... Has original jack and handle,all owners manuals,Sales receipts.service books etc.. This car is a pleasure to drive and I was touring recently at 80mph ..... Smooth and no vibration... There is no rust ever-perfect floor pans and rockers,etc. There is a small rust hole directly below the battery +post and I will repair tomorrow..Very minor about 1" round.. There is a new muffler installed... This car was painted with a medium quality paint job in the 90's and still looks good but i would expect it to be repainted properly with a better repair on the right rear fender,which is a poor repair of what was minor damage......An excellent driver just as it is... Transmission is flawless-shifts smooth and excellent synchros... Currently Registered and clear title.. I have experience shipping and will deliver this car to West Coast Shipping in Richmond CA. for $50... Shipping to most European ports is about $1300...
